   DEBUG: 2026-03-21 16:19:19,583:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | montype | BYTE | 1 | Specifies the
   DEBUG: 2026-03-21 16:19:19,584:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: physiologic meaning of the track. MON
   DEBUG: 2026-03-21 16:19:19,585:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: _
